title: 10/04/21 DPS Hour 3 Carson Palmer
itunes:title: 10/04/21 DPS Hour 3 Carson Palmer
description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, it's the third installment of NFL Week 4 reaction--including the impressive win by the Arizona Cardinals over the Los Angeles Rams. Also, former NFL quarterback and Heisman trophy winner Carson Palmer joins the program to offer his reflections from Tampa Bay at New England as well as other reactions from the professional gridiron.
